# Draft:The Amistad Rebellion: An Atlantic Odyssey of Slavery and Freedom

The Amistad Rebellion: An Atlantic Odyssey of Slavery and Freedom is a book by Marcus Rediker.
Reception
Barbara Hoffert wrote in the Library Journal that Rediker "tell[s] the story anew, giving greater depth to the Africans' background". The book won a Booklist Editors' Choice award for Adult Books in 2012.
